issue.title: [CF 540] Unable to setup Touch of Karma debuf
issue.body:
Hi guys,

Was trying to setup "Touch of Karma" debuf on ME with no success. Tried all 3 available IDs with no luck. After all got popup saying my addons do too much errors. Can you guys look into that?

I've tried it as warrior if that matters.

Thanks.


> Posted by CurseForge user d9d9 | Imported from CurseForge issue #540 | Raw

comments.body:
First of all, please don't ignore the default ticket template. It exists for a reason.

That said, I can't look into something as vague as that. You need to post the errors that you are getting (the ones that pertain to TMW only, though). If you don't have Lua errors enabled, then you need to enable.

In regards to the icon, please post the export string of what you have tried so far in a new ticket using the template provided.


> Posted by CurseForge user Cybeloras
